headline: Teledyne Delivers 100th Infrared Detector for the Space Development Agency’s Tracking Layer
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., March 04, 2025--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY), a leading provider of advanced imaging solutions, is proud to announce its continuing pattern of on-time and early deliveries for the Space Development Agency's (SDA) proliferated constellation. This week marks the delivery of the 100th large format focal plane module, counting deliveries from the Tranche 0, Tranche 1, and now Tranche 2 tracking layers.
